{"schema": {"fields":[{"type":"integer","name":"index"},{"type":"string","name":"author_association"},{"type":"string","name":"body"},{"type":"datetime","name":"created_at"},{"type":"string","name":"html_url"},{"type":"integer","name":"id"},{"type":"string","name":"issue_url"},{"type":"string","name":"node_id"},{"type":"datetime","name":"updated_at"},{"type":"string","name":"url"},{"type":"string","name":"user"}],"pandas_version":"0.20.0","primaryKey":["index"]}, "data": [{"index":0,"author_association":"COLLABORATOR","body":"What is your use case for this change?","created_at":"2018-03-01T15:24:07.000Z","html_url":"https:\/\/github.com\/mrdoob\/three.js\/pull\/13465#issuecomment-369626543","id":369626543,"issue_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/mrdoob\/three.js\/issues\/13465","node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDM2OTYyNjU0Mw==","updated_at":"2018-03-01T15:24:07.000Z","url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/mrdoob\/three.js\/issues\/comments\/369626543","user":{"following_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/Mugen87\/following{\/other_user}","events_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/Mugen87\/events{\/privacy}","avatar_url":"https:\/\/avatars2.githubusercontent.com\/u\/12612165?v=4","url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/Mugen87","gists_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/Mugen87\/gists{\/gist_id}","html_url":"https:\/\/github.com\/Mugen87","subscriptions_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/Mugen87\/subscriptions","node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjEyNjEyMTY1","repos_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/Mugen87\/repos","received_events_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/Mugen87\/received_events","gravatar_id":"","starred_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/Mugen87\/starred{\/owner}{\/repo}","site_admin":false,"login":"Mugen87","type":"User","id":12612165,"followers_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/Mugen87\/followers","organizations_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/Mugen87\/orgs"}},{"index":1,"author_association":"NONE","body":"> What is your use case for this change?\r\n\r\nI want to be able to draw the same geometry with lots of textures, and to enforce the rendering order of each texture (see https:\/\/github.com\/peppsac\/itowns2\/commit\/b61e63d0811dcdc6a934df8211432436014aaa80: it's not finished but the goal is to move away from a single material with N texture uniforms to N groups using 1 texture uniform each)\r\n\r\nAnd regardless of my own usage, each group of geometry.groups is rendered as an individual entity so I think it makes sense to be able to control the renderOrder of each of them.\r\n\r\n(an alternative to this PR would be to move the renderOrder property to Material, but it's a much bigger change)","created_at":"2018-03-01T15:35:04.000Z","html_url":"https:\/\/github.com\/mrdoob\/three.js\/pull\/13465#issuecomment-369630212","id":369630212,"issue_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/mrdoob\/three.js\/issues\/13465","node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDM2OTYzMDIxMg==","updated_at":"2018-03-01T15:35:04.000Z","url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/mrdoob\/three.js\/issues\/comments\/369630212","user":{"following_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/peppsac\/following{\/other_user}","events_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/peppsac\/events{\/privacy}","avatar_url":"https:\/\/avatars3.githubusercontent.com\/u\/2198295?v=4","url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/peppsac","gists_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/peppsac\/gists{\/gist_id}","html_url":"https:\/\/github.com\/peppsac","subscriptions_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/peppsac\/subscriptions","node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjIxOTgyOTU=","repos_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/peppsac\/repos","received_events_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/peppsac\/received_events","gravatar_id":"","starred_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/peppsac\/starred{\/owner}{\/repo}","site_admin":false,"login":"peppsac","type":"User","id":2198295,"followers_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/peppsac\/followers","organizations_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/peppsac\/orgs"}},{"index":2,"author_association":"OWNER","body":"For that use case, why don't you do..\r\n\r\n```js\r\nvar geometry = new THREE.BufferGeometry();\r\nvar group = new THREE.Group();\r\nfor ( var i = 0; i < 10; i ++ ) {\r\n    var material = new THREE.MeshBasicMaterial( { color: 0xffffff * Math.random() } );\r\n    var mesh = new THREE.Mesh( geometry, material );\r\n    mesh.renderOrder = i \/ 10;\r\n    group.add( mesh );\r\n}\r\nscene.add( group );\r\n```","created_at":"2018-03-01T23:31:41.000Z","html_url":"https:\/\/github.com\/mrdoob\/three.js\/pull\/13465#issuecomment-369768336","id":369768336,"issue_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/mrdoob\/three.js\/issues\/13465","node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDM2OTc2ODMzNg==","updated_at":"2018-03-01T23:31:58.000Z","url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/repos\/mrdoob\/three.js\/issues\/comments\/369768336","user":{"following_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/mrdoob\/following{\/other_user}","events_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/mrdoob\/events{\/privacy}","avatar_url":"https:\/\/avatars0.githubusercontent.com\/u\/97088?v=4","url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/mrdoob","gists_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/mrdoob\/gists{\/gist_id}","html_url":"https:\/\/github.com\/mrdoob","subscriptions_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/mrdoob\/subscriptions","node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjk3MDg4","repos_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/mrdoob\/repos","received_events_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/mrdoob\/received_events","gravatar_id":"","starred_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/mrdoob\/starred{\/owner}{\/repo}","site_admin":false,"login":"mrdoob","type":"User","id":97088,"followers_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/mrdoob\/followers","organizations_url":"https:\/\/api.github.com\/users\/mrdoob\/orgs"}},{"index":3,"author_association":"NONE","body":"@mrdoob yep, it's another possibility.\r\n\r\nI still think it can be useful to control groups render o